{"tid":607349,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「幻視」保羅畢特利拆解Marvel成功方程式","createTime":"2018-03-27T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T13:21:40.000Z","uid":105567,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b92ba212bb94f052f6ce9a0caa2e8b218bd5a81","tid":607349,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"Marvel電影成功方程式好多片商都想複製，但似乎冇乜邊間做到。《復仇者聯盟：無限之戰》「幻視」保羅畢特利（Paul Bettany）參與其中，自然有一番見解，佢認為Marvel成功係因為作品由真正嘅fans製作。<br />\n保羅畢特利受訪時表示，製作團隊對一眾角色「有愛」，佢形容當佢第一次穿上幻視裝束時，Marvel Studios總裁Kevin Feige「差啲感動到喊」。雖然保羅畢特利自認本身並非漫畫fans，但漸漸受團隊對原著故事嘅熱愛對所感染，令佢嘅演出更加投入；同時亦使到觀眾們較易接受故事改編嘅變動，因為佢哋深信團隊係為故事表現得更好而改進。<br />\n<br />\n 資料來源:Screenrant<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26356&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D26356%26catid%3D35&d=kVF0zWoN3lybMO8wK4pXWtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=26bc4b7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26356&amp;catid=35</a>"},{"pid":"f7d6dfa18543290eb4fb4496c913bfa342c88699","tid":607349,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/15/c1/7f/15c17f18f2d16e684fbfdf7fa13742bb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F15%2Fc1%2F7f%2F15c17f18f2d16e684fbfdf7fa13742bb.gif&h=5acb1c34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53db174dcfe8e4446115fcadb57b08ba08401fc0","tid":607349,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f7d6dfa18543290eb4fb4496c913bfa342c88699","tid":607349,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/15/c1/7f/15c17f18f2d16e684fbfdf7fa13742bb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F15%2Fc1%2F7f%2F15c17f18f2d16e684fbfdf7fa1374